    <string name="onboarding_welcome_title">DiLink-Auto ga xush kelibsiz</string>
    <string name="onboarding_welcome_desc">Telefon ilovalaridan avtomobilning ichki ekranida foydalaning. Hammasi ishlashi uchun bir nechta ruxsatni sozlaymiz.</string>
    <string name="onboarding_files_title">Barcha fayllarga kirish</string>
    <string name="onboarding_files_desc">Virtual displey serverini telefon xotirasiga joylashtiradi. Busiz avtomobil ekran aks ettirishni boshlay olmaydi.</string>
    <string name="onboarding_battery_title">Batareyani optimallashtirish</string>
    <string name="onboarding_battery_desc">Ekran o\'chiq bo\'lganda ulanishni faol saqlaydi. Busiz telefon uyquga ketganda uzatish to\'xtaydi.</string>
    <string name="onboarding_accessibility_title">Maxsus imkoniyatlar xizmati</string>
    <string name="onboarding_accessibility_desc">Avtomobilning sensorli ekrani telefoningizni boshqarishiga imkon beradi. Busiz ekranni ko\'rasiz, lekin tegina olmaysiz.</string>
    <string name="onboarding_notification_title">Bildirishnomalarga kirish</string>
    <string name="onboarding_notification_desc">Telefon bildirishnomalarini avtomobil displeyida ko\'rsatadi. Busiz haydash paytida qo\'ng\'iroqlar va xabarlarni o\'tkazib yuborasiz.</string>
